{"tid":1023574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"媽媽狂發爆乳淫蕩照吸人氣　羅馬新星求不要再發淫蕩爆乳照","createTime":"2019-02-16T01:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T02:02:45.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60adc42d3de62b8e81d3eb67c33b8c4f2b8dc406","tid":1023574,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"效力於義大利羅馬體育俱樂部的19歲足球員贊尼奧洛(Nicolo Zaniolo)，被視為是新生代的足球明星，外界看好他的未來發展與實力，但最近贊尼奧洛卻對41歲媽媽柯絲塔(Francesca Costa)隔空喊話，要求媽媽不要再發淫蕩爆乳照。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，贊尼奧洛在近幾場比賽中表現不錯，人氣逐漸攀升，被視為是新生代明星。在此同時，贊尼奧洛的媽媽柯絲塔更是一位網紅，人氣不輸給兒子，她的Instagram上已經吸引超過16.9萬名粉絲。而柯絲塔不時上傳爆乳嘟嘴、裝可愛性感的照片，雖然年過40，但還是保有20歲的青春活力。<br />\n<br />\n不過兒子贊尼奧洛卻看不下去，他在其中一張照片上留言：「媽，你不要再發淫蕩照了。你嘴巴幹嘛要那個樣子？你都40歲了！」<br />\n<br />\n柯絲塔的老公，也同樣是足球明星伊格爾(Igor Zaniolo)，也是贊尼奧洛的爸。但報導指出，贊尼奧洛被視為是有「羅馬王子」之稱的足球明星托蒂(Francesco Totti)的接班人，當柯絲塔第一次看到托蒂時，忍不住大哭，她完全說不出話，而伊格爾也在現場，看到這一幕都笑了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190216/1518323/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190216%2F1518323%2F&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=2fe2d903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190216%2F1518323%2F&h=45a9506c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190216/1518323/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190216/640_ba860fe4cc7bdb245d06d2da53fb6226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190216%2F640_ba860fe4cc7bdb245d06d2da53fb6226.jpg&h=af3b48f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190216/640_d7a7bfeadff1f929dfc698b40f857f07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190216%2F640_d7a7bfeadff1f929dfc698b40f857f07.jpg&h=3656b5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190216/640_6ebf49811a60d325630d8ba886ab2354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190216%2F640_6ebf49811a60d325630d8ba886ab2354.jpg&h=7d4ecea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07934d21de7b5cb964d400481daa5b019af841c4","tid":1023574,"uid":56063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:30:30.000Z","msg":"totti有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢老母呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755a2e9e5dc107d9bd4b6fc5fcc444679aae19d2","tid":1023574,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1e6a1dbd6a16c785d941381d996884ae3b02a8","tid":1023574,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"755a2e9e5dc107d9bd4b6fc5fcc444679aae19d2","tid":1023574,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:42:23.000Z","msg":"名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1fe031b13e5f83f329f954ea963f2426cf00c1","tid":1023574,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:43:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/ln